# VHS Script: Heatmap Mode Demo
# Shows GitHub-style activity visualization with color intensity

Output ../images/07-heatmap-mode.gif

# Terminal settings
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 0.05s

# Start the program
Type "ccu"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# Switch to heatmap mode
Type "h"
Sleep 4s

# Stay on heatmap to show the visualization
Sleep 2s

# Exit
Type "q"
Sleep 1s
